Tokyo Stocks Rise
</SUBHEAD>
<P>
   TOKYO (AP) -- The Nikkei rose 182.54 points to 18,156.24 points at the end of
the morning trading. On Friday, the Dow climbed 154.19 to close at 10,733.91.
</P>
