<HEADLINE> 'U-571' Tops Box Office Again  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES (AP) -- The submarine film ''U-571'' sank the
box-office competition again, taking in $12.2 million during its
second weekend.
</P>
